ActIndian Act
SubjectTsartlip First Nations ** DESIGNATION ** For leasing purposes
PrecisOrder accepting a DESIGNATION by the TSARTLIP FIRST NATION, for a term of 99 years, of approximately 4.423 hectares (10.93 acres) of land on South Saanich Indian Reserve No. 1, in British Columbia, for leasing purposes.
